48:34.833 --> 48:36.958
[beeps]

48:39.667 --> 48:40.875
[Arthur] Ay, hindi.

48:41.917 --> 48:43.958
Hindi, hindi, hindi, hindi. Hindi.

48:48.875 --> 48:50.250
[umiiyak] Tootles.

48:57.208 --> 48:59.208
-[beeps]
-[Arthur] Tootles.

